node.title: Transmission tangle leaves Coromandel region without power
node.description: Power has been cut to most of the Coromandel region after plastic wrap became tangled in a transmission line.
node.content:
["Power has been cut to most of the Coromandel region after plastic wrap became tangled in a transmission line.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly\n
", "Transpower says to remove the plastic safely, it needs to turn off the power.", "\"This is a hazard that could cause a fire or unexpected electricity outage,\" it said.", "The power will be off from 10am until 1pm this afternoon in the Matatoki, Thames, Whitianga, Tairua, Kerepehi and Coromandel areas."]
